snippet.title: RV Newbie Lessons - Choose Your Spot Wisely
snippet.description:
It was a week for catching up on essential tasks like laundry, refilling propane and getting the oil changed. After showing up to our spot, we learned quickly that we probably don't want to find ourselves in a similar situation again.

Things we discuss or show that contribute to the enjoyment of full-time rv'ing are linked below!

This video was not sponsored by anybody and we have no affiliation with any of the products or companies we discuss in this video. Links are provided below for anyone interested in learning more about what we use and we may earn a small commission should you purchase through these links.
